<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
    <BANWlLib.BaDef.PunaraSpine>
        <defName>BANW_PunaraSpine</defName>
        <onClickspineAnimationNames>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>13</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex>Mouth_10</defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\onClick1.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>false</isBlink>
                <text>混乱，是无法理解的行动。\n请不要再戳了。\n会故障的。</text>
            </li>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>16</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex>Mouth_03</defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\onClick2.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>在这里可以进行老师的各种工作。</text>
            </li>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>04</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex>Mouth_05</Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex>Mouth_10</defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\onClick3.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>我明白了，老师现在\n没有特别想做的事情吧。\n很闲对吧。</text>
            </li>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>18</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex>Mouth_03</defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\onClick4.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>老师\n请选择想要进行的工作。</text>
            </li>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>18</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex>Mouth_03</defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\onClick5.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>必须解决的工作还有很多。\n那么，就拜托您了。</text>
            </li>
           
        </onClickspineAnimationNames>
        <startClickspineAnimationNames>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>15</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex>Mouth_03</defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\Start1.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>连接确认 老师，\n让你久等了</text>
            </li>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>15</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex>Mouth_03</defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\Start2.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>该开始工作了。</text>
            </li>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>02</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex></defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\Start3.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>要开始哪个工作呢，老师。</text>
            </li>
            <li>
                <spineAnimationName>02</spineAnimationName>
                <Mouth_Tex></Mouth_Tex>
                <defMouse_Tex></defMouse_Tex>
                <aronaAudioClipPath>Sounds\punaraAudio\Start4.ogg</aronaAudioClipPath>
                <isBlink>true</isBlink>
                <text>待机中。\n必须解决的作业仍存在许多。</text>
            </li>
        </startClickspineAnimationNames>
    </BANWlLib.BaDef.PunaraSpine>
</Defs>
